## 8. Relationship Between OPRMT™, PCE, and DOAS™

OPRMT™ defines the structure.

Prompt Compliance Engineering evaluates whether prompts and outputs comply with defined requirements.

DOAS™ may provide a scoring model for evaluating how well a prompt or output satisfies structured criteria.

```text
OPRMT™ = Structure
PCE = Compliance Review
DOAS™ = Scoring and Assessment
```

